# 📚 MASTER NARRATIVE AUDIT: THE PLATONIC VERSES

**Status:** Vitrified Audit | **Structure:** 4/52/+ | **Version:** 1.0

This document maps the existing 61+ chapters and fragments of the *Platonic Verses* to the formal **4/52/+ Architecture** requested for the Sovereign 1.0 Release.

---

## I. THE 4 PROLOGUES (The Algebraic-Geometric Bedrock)
These chapters establish the "theory" of the universe before the annual cycle begins. They are currently housed in `The_Platonic_Verses_Book_1.md`.

| Position | Chapter Name | Geometric Focus | Narrative Beat |
|----------|--------------|-----------------|----------------|
| **0** | **The Void** | 0 / Zero | Hades invents the shadow; Zeus hates the placeholder. |
